### Block CSS comment header — required on every block

```css
/*
==========================================================
BLOCK NAME — block-name.css
==========================================================
WHAT IT IS:
Brief description.

WHAT IT DOES:
Brief description.

HOW TO USE:
1. Step one
2. Step two

All values use boilerplate CSS tokens from style.css.
==========================================================
*/
```

